text: Giorgiana "Dana" Carteleanu (born December 18, 1979) is a Romanian rhythmic gymnast. Stoica competed for Romania in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all-around competition at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. There she was 32nd in the qualification and didn't advance to the semifinal. == References == == External links == * * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania
